title: Markets and Coronavirus, SC Primary Preview
itunes:title: Markets and Coronavirus, SC Primary Preview
description:
Kevin spoke to Nareit Senior Economist Calvin Schnure about concern over the spread of the Coronavirus that sent U.S. stocks to their worst week since the financial crisis.


Panel guests: Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative Media, Eli Yokley, Political reporter for Morning Consult and Marc Ross, CEO of Caracal Global.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
